title: (1999-2015) Best of MUSE
description:
Muse is a three-man alternative rock band that started in 1994 and took off in 1999. Their songwriter, Matthew Bellamy, is a Mozart on piano and a musical genius when it comes to riffs, chords, arrangement, and lyrics. He is accompanied by bassist Chris Wolstenholme and drummer Dominic Howard. This is not an official compilation, and all music is owned by Muse.
